'''圖書存放處'''（{{lang-en|'''Book Depository'''}}，曾用名「The Book Depository」）是一間[[英國|英國]]網絡書店，擁有大規模的圖書目錄，並提供免費郵寄至超過160個國家。<ref>{{Citation | title = Help | url = https://www.bookdepository.com/help/topic/HelpId/3/Which-countries-do-you-deliver-to#helpContent | contribution = Which countries do you deliver to? | publisher = The Book depository | accessdate = 2021-03-21 | archive-date = 2020-09-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200917012159/https://www.bookdepository.com/help/topic/HelpId/3/Which-countries-do-you-deliver-to#helpContent }}.</ref>書店是由前[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]僱員創立。2011年，該店被亞馬遜收購。<ref>{{Citation | publisher = The Book Depository | title = Help | contribution = How does the Amazon acquisition affect The Book Depository customers? | url = http://www.bookdepository.com/help/topic/HelpId/54/How-does-the-Amazon-acquisition-affect-The-Book-Depository-customers#helpContent | accessdate = 2021-03-21 | archive-date = 2016-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161011054949/http://www.bookdepository.com/help/topic/HelpId/54/How-does-the-Amazon-acquisition-affect-The-Book-Depository-customers#helpContent }}.</ref>

== 歷史 ==
該公司由{{link-en|安德魯·克勞佛|Andrew Crawford (entrepreneur)}}和現任首席運營官Stuart Felton於2004年創立。其座右銘是「[[長尾|All Books Available to All]]」。

2011年7月4日，[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]達成協議收購圖書存放處。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.theguardian.com/books/2011/jul/05/amazon-the-book-depository |title = Booksellers fear 'stranglehold' as Amazon snaps up British rival The Book Depository |author = Zoe Wood |date = 2011-07-05 |publisher = The Guardian |language = en |accessdate = 2017-01-31 |archive-date = 2018-12-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181225045420/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2011/jul/05/amazon-the-book-depository+ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

